{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "allowJs": true,
    "allowSyntheticDefaultImports": true,
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "declaration": true,
    "emitDeclarationOnly": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "jsx": "react",
    "module": "commonjs",
    "moduleResolution": "node",
    "noImplicitAny": true,
    "outDir": "typings",
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "sourceMap": true,
    "strictNullChecks": true,
    "target": "esnext",
    "types": ["node"],
  },
  "include": ["lib", ".eslintrc.cjs"],
}
